20240117
========
- Changed old -x argument to -l
- Added new -x argument which causes copying of extended attributes.
- Changed default verbosity level from 0 to 1.
- Added sync() call at the end.

20240307
========
- If a symlink already exists but is pointing to something else it now won't be
  updated unless -c option given.
- Added more counts at end.
- Now doesn't sync if nothing copied.
- Updated some of the code to C++17.
- Minor bug fixes.

20240801
========
- Fixed bug whereby it wasn't deleting unmatched files in a directory where
  there were no files to add.
- Changed -l option to slightly more logical -u (for unlink).
- Minor updates.
